          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Thomas M.</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">CTO · Agence digitale, 28 personnes</div>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
        <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-3">
          <% 5.times do %>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          "L'onboarding de nos nouveaux devs prenait 2 semaines à organiser. Avec Izi-RH, je crée le template une fois, je le réutilise à chaque arrivée. Gain de temps massif."
        </blockquote>
        <figcaption class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-violet-100 dark:bg-violet-900/40 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400">RC</div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Romain C.</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">VP Engineering · Scale-up, 55 personnes</div>
          </div>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <figure class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
        <div class="flex gap-0.5 mb-3">
          <% 5.times do %>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          <% end %>
